comments.comment:
gates ashutoshc can you please take a look? I wanted to fix this everywhere but that's too much pain.
Catalog support seems really brittle right now. Ideally we should eliminate the usage of IMetaStoreClient apis missing catalog name from everywhere. Hive.java can handle current-catalog. For now this just fixes an issue with alter-partition.

Here are the results of testing the latest attachment:
https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12935957/HIVE-20411.patch
